_header: That man is wise and well fortunate
_description: ‘Þe seynge of wyse men’ — one 7-line and one 6-line stanzas

BodAsh59.First Lines:
þat man is wys and weele fortunateþat by oþer men
                    can leorne to eschieveþe grete meschieves of þe wreched
                    fatefful sooþe it is and may not be vntruwe…
BodAsh59.Last Lines:
…He may be cleped felix men may defiyseþus may harme be
                    cleped profitable
